## Additional Notices

This project incorporates and builds upon several open source technologies:

- **AdalFlow**: For automatic prompt optimization
- **ChromaDB**: For vector database functionality  
- **FastAPI**: For web framework
- **Neo4j**: For knowledge graph database
- **Ollama**: For local LLM inference

Special thanks to KITECH (Korea Institute of Industrial Technology) for 
supporting the research and development of root industry applications.

## Korean Root Industries Focus

This software is specifically designed for and optimized for the Korean 
root industries (뿌리산업):
- 주조 (Casting)
- 금형 (Molding) 
- 소성가공 (Plastic Working)
- 용접 (Welding)
- 표면처리 (Surface Treatment)
- 열처리 (Heat Treatment)

The Korean language processing and industry-specific optimizations are
integral parts of this system and are provided under the same MIT license.